        <tr><td>Norway</td><td>−NOK 4.1m/person (R3 group)</td><td>Asylum &amp; non-European family migration, net present value</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Germany</td><td>−€2.1bn/year</td><td>2015 refugee cohort</td></tr>
